====Definitions====
{{head|zh|hanzi}}

# to [[grasp]]; to [[hold]]; to [[clutch]]
# to [[catch]]; to [[capture]]
#: {{zh-x|他們 捉 到 了 幾 條 魚。|They '''caught''' several fish.}}
#: {{zh-x|小 雛雞 圍 在 母雞 的 周圍 捉 蟲子{zi}。|The baby chicks are '''catching''' insects around the hen.}}
# to [[tease]]; to [[play]] [[tricks]] on
# to [[arrest]] (a person for a crime); to [[apprehend]]
# {{lb|zh|Cantonese}} to [[arrest]] for a [[crime]]
#: {{zh-co|捉 違泊{paak3}|to '''prosecute''' illegal parking|C}}
# {{lb|zh|Cantonese|Hakka}} to [[play]] (a board game)
#: {{zh-co|捉 象棋|tr='''zog5''' xiong4 ki2|to '''play''' [[Chinese chess]]|H-MX}}
# {{lb|zh|Wu}} to [[pick]]; to [[pluck]]
#: {{zh-x|捉 花|tr=sh:'''7tsoq'''&1ho|to '''pick''' cotton|SH}}
# {{lb|zh|Wu}} to [[pick up]]; to [[collect]]
#: {{zh-x|捉 蹔[𫏐]𧉆|tr=sh:'''7tsoq'''&6ze ciq|to '''pick up''' cigarette butts ''(figuratively)''|SH}}
